Package ui.customers

package ui.customers
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    CustomerAddPage
    CustomerAddPage is the pop-up displayed in the application to add new Customer
    CustomerAddPageButtons
    CustomerAddPageButtons are the submit and cancel buttons on the add customer form.
    CustomerComboBox
    CustomerComboBox is a comboBox containing a list of Countries
    CustomerEditPage
    CustomerEditPage is the pop-up page displayed to edit an existing customer.
    CustomerEditPageButtons
    CustomerEditPageButtons are the submit and cancel buttons on the edit customer form.
    CustomerInfoForm
    CustomerInfoForm contains the fields for adding or updating a Customer.
    CustomerTableControls
    CustomerTableControls contains the buttons for interacting with the data stored in the table.
    CustomerTablePane
    CustomerTablePane contains the buttons and tableview displayed in the application.
    CustomerTableView
    CustomerTableView displays a table containing all customer documents stored in the database.
